---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Team
seo:
  title: Meet the Vandore Heritage Team
  description: Learn more about the strategists, conservation partners, and hospitality specialists at Vandore Heritage.
_enabled_editors:
  - visual
  - data
hero:
  eyebrow: The team
  headline: Specialists aligned around your goals
  subheadline: Vandore Heritage blends strategy, hospitality, and conservation expertise to deliver bespoke outcomes.
  cta_label: Talk with us
  cta_url: /contact/
intro:
  text: Our core team is supported by a trusted collective of architects, legal advisors, and cultural partners across the Baltics and beyond.
people:
  - name: Laura Vandore
    title: Founder & Lead Strategist
    focus: Stewardship of heritage transactions, executive briefings, and partnership alignment.
  - name: Martins Ozols
    title: Head of Client Experience
    focus: Designing relocation programs and concierge services for executive households.
  - name: Ieva Kravale
    title: Conservation Partnerships
    focus: Sourcing craftspeople, overseeing restoration quality, and ensuring narrative continuity.
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p data-cms-bind="#hero.eyebrow">{{ hero.eyebrow }}</p>
    <h1 data-cms-bind="#hero.headline">{{ hero.headline }}</h1>
    <p data-cms-bind="#hero.subheadline">{{ hero.subheadline }}</p>
    <a class="cta" href="{{ hero.cta_url }}"><span data-cms-bind="#hero.cta_label">{{ hero.cta_label }}</span></a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p data-cms-bind="#intro.text">{{ intro.text }}</p>
    <div class="grid two">
      {% for person in people %}
      <article class="card" data-cms-collection="people" data-cms-item="{{ loop.index0 }}">
        <h2 data-cms-bind="name">{{ person.name }}</h2>
        <p class="meta" data-cms-bind="title">{{ person.title }}</p>
        <p data-cms-bind="focus">{{ person.focus }}</p>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

